overview: Emily Da Vinci is a cute, red haired Canadian girl... but don't be fooled by her innocent looks! Axel Braun might be the coach, but she definitely is the captain of this incredible team o'whores! Foxy Lady must be the second-in-command, since she takes an impromptu first time double-vag with the ease f a pro, speaking of pros, please give it up for fan-favorite Missy Monroe, lending a hand.. and much more, to debutante Aurianna in a two-against-two with Mr. Pete and Marco Duato. The team is ready to play... are you?
title: Double Teamed 5
